OL,3,CRelief and joy for workers as historic
OL,4,Cshipyard is saved by rescue deal
OL,6,FITV News' Sam Blackledge reports from
OL,7,FNorth Devon as jobs are saved at
OL,8,FAppledore.
OL,10,FPeople in the North Devon village of
OL,11,FAppledore say they are "thrilled" that
OL,12,Ftheir historic shipyard has been saved
OL,13,Fby a rescue deal.
OL,15,FSpanish shipbuilding firm Navantia has
OL,16,Fagreed to buy Harland and Wolff,
OL,17,Fsecuring the future of the Appledore
OL,18,Fyard.
