OL,3,CRelief and joy for workers as historic
OL,4,Cshipyard is saved by rescue deal
OL,6,FAnnouncing the deal in the House of
OL,7,FCommons on Thursday morning, Business
OL,8,FSecretary Jonathan Reynolds said:
OL,9,F"This industry-led deal, which we
OL,10,Fexpect to complete shortly, will
OL,11,Fsecure all four of Harland and Wolff's
OL,12,Fshipyards, protecting around 1,000
OL,13,Fjobs right across the UK.
OL,15,F"I hope this announcement will come as
OL,16,Fsome relief to Harland and Wolff's
OL,17,Femployees. I realise this has been a
OL,18,Fdeeply worrying time for them and for
OL,19,Feveryone affected by the continued
OL,20,Fspeculation over the firm's future."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
