OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey added:
OL,7,F"This agreement keeps vital defence
OL,8,Fmanufacturing in the UK and protects
OL,9,Fskilled jobs at historic shipyards
OL,10,Facross our nations.
OL,12,F"It strengthens our sovereign
OL,13,Fcapability to support Royal Navy
OL,14,Foperations worldwide, while building
OL,15,Fthe industrial partnerships that will
OL,16,Fdrive growth."
OL,18,FJosie Tennant, who runs the Royal
OL,19,FGeorge Inn in the heart of Appledore,
OL,20,Fsays the shipyard is a vital part of
OL,21,Fthe region.
