OL,3,CRelief and joy for workers as historic
OL,4,Cshipyard is saved by rescue deal
OL,6,F"We have a lot of locals who work for
OL,7,Fthe shipyard and I know it's been a
OL,8,Fworry to them over the last months and
OL,9,Fyears, while things have been all over
OL,10,Fthe place.
OL,12,F"We're really pleased going into the
OL,13,FNew Year that people can feel safe and
OL,14,Fsecure in their jobs and hopefully
OL,15,Fthis means the security of the
OL,16,Fshipyard for many years to come."
