OL,3,CRelief and joy for workers as historic
OL,4,Cshipyard is saved by rescue deal
OL,6,FJust a few years ago, GMB members were
OL,7,Fmarching against plans to close the
OL,8,Fyard. The union's national officer,
OL,9,FMatthew Roberts, says more positive
OL,10,Ftalks have already begun.
OL,12,F"We will be going into consultation
OL,13,Fbetween the trade unions and the
OL,14,Fincoming employer," he said.
